- "Roots are ZORP to tree, as foundation is ZORP to building"
- "Pilot is ZORP to airplane, as captain is ZORP to ship"
Your Task:
1. Complete this analogy using ZORP: "Keyboard is ZORP to computer, as _______ is ZORP to _______"
2. Define what ZORP means:

